memberdef.name: META_REGISTER_GROUP
memberdef.initializer: FGuid GroupName; \ do \ { \ const FMetaGroupSettings* const GroupSettings = GroupsDefaultSettings.Find(EMetaLayerGroupType::GroupName); \ if (!GroupSettings) \ { \ META_LOG(LogMetaLayersComponent, Error, TEXT("Group: [%s]. GroupSettings is invalid!"), TEXT(#GroupName)); \ break; \ } \ \ if (GroupSettings->bEnabled) \ { \ GroupName = RegisterGroup( \ LOCTABLE("Layers", #GroupName), \ GroupSettings->bToggleable, \ GroupSettings->bEnabledByDefault \ ); \ } \ } while (false)
